casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of Warren Jay BRONSNICK.
No. D-2919.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 6, 2017.
Warren Jay Bronsnick, of Short Hills, New Jersey, having requested to resign as a member of the Bar of this Court, it is ordered that his name be stricken from the roll of attorneys admitted to the practice of law before this Court. The Rule to Show Cause, issued on August 8, 2016, is discharged.
